{"tid":1479941,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【業主大行動】按揭與中銀","createTime":"2019-08-17T05:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T06:27:40.000Z","uid":86592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"03a224fcffc31f8f3e111180c918018eea9a6450","tid":1479941,"uid":86592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:56:39.000Z","msg":"而家本地市場<br />\n基本上中銀就係大贏家<br />\n按揭業務對一間銀行極其重要<br />\n你一定識得揀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVYZ3Nv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVYZ3Nv.jpg&h=82bdea1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFcHg6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFcHg6G.jpg&h=683384eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大型銀行今年中起調整按揭優惠，現樓按揭巿佔率冠軍亦出現執位情況，中銀香港7月份現樓按揭巿佔率升至高達26.8%，超越連續28個單月冠軍的滙豐銀行，成為現樓按揭巿佔率一哥；滙豐銀行於樓花按揭巿場維持十連冠。"},{"pid":"e47ab8eba628fa292161cc2c852dc4a05dcdde75","tid":1479941,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"牆內微博今天這轉發江，93歲生日祝福，普遍+1來祝福！93了，不小了，李鵬還沒走多遠，趕緊的！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQ7j3UQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQ7j3UQ.jpg&h=63487db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江sir幾時去見毛蠟像 同 李sir吖？？？？"},{"pid":"c9e2105ccf6f29214b62e6331bf5fdaf74021b05","tid":1479941,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:27:40.000Z","msg":"有時唔係揀唔揀, <br />\n而係有啲銀行極其保守, 估唔足價, <br />\n點揀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}